SSAO Attendance Monitoring System
For our final project we have assigned to create a system that will monitor and record the attendance of every student in such event so that the School or the teacher can monitor weather the student is absent. This system includes adding of event, creating of user who can manipulate in recording the attendance of every students, it also supports the admin user so that the other settings cannot be manipulated by the user .This system also includes adding of students for the purpose of recording their attendance by the use of their ID. This system will monitor the time when the student exactly Sign In/Out. In signing In/out the student will know if he/she is truly attended an event because it will notify his/her name after he/she signed In/Out. The record can be viewed either by student attended activity only, all student records, by course, selected course in every year level, and all course every year level. This System is created using Microsoft Visual Studio 2008 and is also supported by the use of MS Access 2007 for the database, and also Crystal report for the print of the reports.
